### 2. Definitions / 定义

"Covered Software" means the Software, any copy or portion of the Software, and any modification, derivative work, adaptation, translation, refactoring, reimplementation, restatement, port, replacement, compiled version, object-code version, minified version, obfuscated version, containerized version, hosted instance, dataset entry, embedding, vector representation, index, prompt, retrieval source, benchmark item, or other material that contains, is based on, is derived from, is generated from, is extracted from, or incorporates any material part of the Software.

“受覆盖软件”指本软件、本软件的任何副本或部分，以及任何包含、基于、衍生自、生成自、提取自或并入本软件任何实质部分的修改、衍生作品、适配、翻译、重构、重新实现、重述、移植、替代实现、编译版本、目标代码版本、压缩版本、混淆版本、容器化版本、托管实例、数据集条目、嵌入、向量表示、索引、提示、检索源、基准项目或其他材料。

Covered Software includes reimplementation, port, replacement, or restatement substantially derived from, or materially informed by access to, review of, or use of, the structure, sequence, organization, logic, design, schema, interface, or expressive content of the Software, even if a different programming language, architecture, formatting, naming, or surface expression is used, to the maximum extent permitted by law.

受覆盖软件包括在法律允许的最大范围内，实质性衍生自，或因访问、审阅或使用本软件的结构、顺序、组织、逻辑、设计、模式、接口或表达内容而获得实质性信息的重新实现、移植、替代实现或重述，即使其使用不同的编程语言、架构、格式、命名或表层表达。

For embeddings, vector representations, indexes, prompts, retrieval sources, benchmarks, model artifacts, outputs, and similar materials, coverage applies to the extent such material contains, encodes, preserves, reproduces, is substantially derived from, or is used as a substitute for expressive content of the Software.

对于嵌入、向量表示、索引、提示、检索源、基准、模型制品、输出及类似材料，仅在其包含、编码、保留、复制、实质性衍生自或被用作本软件表达内容替代品的范围内，构成受覆盖软件。

Incidental, remote, or de minimis relationships do not by themselves create Covered Software.

偶然、遥远或极小的关联本身不构成受覆盖软件。

"AI/ML System" means any artificial intelligence system, machine learning system, neural network, foundation model, large language model, generative model, agent, model, service, platform, application, feature, pipeline, retrieval system, embedding system, automated code-analysis system, automated code-generation system, or substantially similar computational or statistical system.

“AI/ML 系统”指任何人工智能系统、机器学习系统、神经网络、基础模型、大语言模型、生成式模型、智能体、模型、服务、平台、应用、功能、流水线、检索系统、嵌入系统、自动代码分析系统、自动代码生成系统，或任何实质性类似的计算或统计系统。

AI/ML System does not include deterministic developer tools, including without limitation compilers, linkers, linters, formatters, build tools, version-control systems, regular-expression search, or deterministic static-analysis tools, that do not perform statistical inference, model training, generative output, semantic embedding, or neural-network processing.

AI/ML 系统不包括（包括但不限于）确定性的编译器、链接器、代码检查器、格式化工具、构建工具、版本控制系统、正则表达式搜索，或不执行统计推断、模型训练、生成式输出、语义嵌入或神经网络处理的确定性静态分析工具。

Incidental non-model heuristics or non-adaptive ranking do not by themselves make a tool an AI/ML System absent learned or statistical inference materially affecting outputs.

在没有实质影响输出的学习式或统计推断的情况下，偶然的非模型启发式规则或非自适应排序本身不使工具构成 AI/ML 系统。

"Licensor" means each copyright holder of the Software or any person or entity that offers Covered Software under this License.

“许可人”指本软件的每一版权持有人，或依据本许可证提供受覆盖软件的任何个人或实体。

"Restricted Person" means any natural person, legal person, entity, organization, agency, instrumentality, affiliate, subsidiary, parent, successor, assignee, contractor, subcontractor, agent, nominee, trustee, or person coordinating to evade or facilitate evasion of this License that satisfies any of the following:

“受限主体”指符合以下任一条件的任何自然人、法人、实体、组织、机构（含机关）、关联方、子公司、母公司、继承人、受让人、承包商、分包商、代理人、名义持有人、受托人，或为规避或便利规避本许可证而协调行动的人：

1. is organized, incorporated, registered, domiciled, resident, headquartered, principally managed, or principally operating in or under the laws of the United States of America or the State of Israel;

   依据美利坚合众国或以色列国法律设立、成立、注册，或住所、居住地、总部、主要管理地或主要经营地位于美利坚合众国或以色列国；

2. is a citizen, national, permanent resident, or lawful resident of the United States of America or the State of Israel;

   为美利坚合众国或以色列国的公民、国民、永久居民或合法居民；

3. is directly or indirectly owned, controlled, majority-owned, beneficially owned, directed, managed, or materially influenced by any person described in paragraph 1 or 2, including where such person holds at least twenty-five percent (25%) of equity, voting power, beneficial ownership, profit interest, governance rights, veto rights, appointment rights, or rights to direct AI/ML, software, data, product, security, or technical decisions;

   由第 1 项或第 2 项所述主体直接或间接拥有、控制、多数持股、受益拥有、指挥、管理或实质影响，包括该等主体持有至少百分之二十五（25%）的股权、表决权、受益所有权、利润权益、治理权、否决权、任命权，或有权指挥 AI/ML、软件、数据、产品、安全或技术决策的情形；

4. directly or indirectly owns, controls, majority-owns, beneficially owns, directs, manages, or materially influences any person described in paragraph 1, 2, or 3, using the same thresholds and rights described in paragraph 3;

   直接或间接拥有、控制、多数持股、受益拥有、指挥、管理或实质影响第 1、2 或 3 项所述主体，并适用第 3 项所述相同门槛和权利标准；

5. has in any position with authority over AI/ML, software, data, product, security, technical roadmap, licensing, or compliance decisions any person described in paragraph 1 or 2, including without limitation any director, officer, senior manager, general partner, managing member, chief executive, chief operating officer, chief financial officer, chief technology officer, chief information officer, chief data officer, chief AI officer, chief scientist, principal researcher, or substantially equivalent position;

   在任何对 AI/ML、软件、数据、产品、安全、技术路线、许可或合规决策具有权限的职位上，由第 1 项或第 2 项所述主体担任，包括但不限于董事、高级管理人员、高级经理、普通合伙人、管理成员、首席执行官、首席运营官、首席财务官、首席技术官、首席信息官、首席数据官、首席 AI 官、首席科学家、主要研究员或实质等同职位；

6. within the preceding sixty (60) months materially performs, has materially performed, bids for, receives material funding or compensation from, supplies material goods or services to, contracts with, subcontracts for, provides material support to, receives material consideration from, or otherwise undertakes material business for or on behalf of the government, military, defense department, armed forces, intelligence agency, security agency, surveillance agency, law-enforcement agency, national-security body, or defense, military, intelligence, security, surveillance, law-enforcement, or national-security contractor or subcontractor of the United States of America or the State of Israel.

   在此前六十（60）个月内，曾经或正在为美利坚合众国或以色列国政府、军方、国防部门、武装力量、情报机构、安全机构、监视机构、执法机构、国家安全机关，或其国防、军事、情报、安全、监视、执法或国家安全承包商或分包商，实质提供服务、投标、获得重大资助或对价、提供实质性货物或服务、承包、分包、提供实质支持、获得实质性对价，或以其他方式承接实质性业务。

Passive ownership solely through a diversified index fund, mutual fund, exchange-traded fund, custodian, broker, depositary, or other non-controlling passive investment vehicle does not by itself make a person a Restricted Person, unless such arrangement is used to evade this License or is accompanied by actual control, direction, board observer rights, advisory rights, governance rights, technical direction, material influence, or Restricted Use.

仅通过多元化指数基金、共同基金、交易所交易基金、托管人、经纪商、存托机构或其他非控制性被动投资工具进行的被动持有，本身不使任何人成为受限主体；但该安排被用于规避本许可证，或伴随实际控制、指挥、董事会观察员权利、顾问权利、治理权、技术指挥、实质影响或受限使用的除外。

Ordinary employment, ordinary consumer use, ordinary sales of generally available goods or services, or de minimis commercial dealings do not by themselves create Restricted Person status absent material decision-making authority, approval rights, practical control, material influence, or Restricted Use.

普通雇佣、普通消费者使用、普通销售通常可获得的商品或服务，或极小商业往来，在不存在实质决策权限、批准权、实际控制、实质影响或受限使用的情况下，本身不构成受限主体身份。

"Control" includes direct or indirect power, by ownership, contract, funding, governance right, veto right, appointment right, board observer right, advisory right, technical dependency, business dependency, or otherwise, to direct, restrain, approve, materially influence, or benefit from the management, policies, operations, technical roadmap, data use, product use, or disposition of a person or entity.

“控制”包括通过所有权、合同、资金、治理权、否决权、任命权、董事会观察员权利、顾问权利、技术依赖、业务依赖或其他方式，直接或间接地指挥、限制、批准、实质影响或受益于某一人或实体的管理、政策、运营、技术路线、数据使用、产品使用或处分的权力。

Control is presumed where a person holds at least twenty-five percent (25%) of equity, voting power, beneficial ownership, profit interest, board-appointment rights, veto rights, or contractual rights over AI/ML, software, data, product, security, technical, licensing, or compliance decisions.

若某人持有至少百分之二十五（25%）的股权、表决权、受益所有权、利润权益、董事任命权、否决权，或对 AI/ML、软件、数据、产品、安全、技术、许可或合规决策享有合同权利，则推定存在控制。

"Restricted AI Use" means any of the following acts involving Covered Software, in whole or in part, directly or indirectly:

“受限 AI 使用”指直接或间接地、全部或部分地涉及受覆盖软件的以下任何行为：

1. training, fine-tuning, aligning, evaluating, validating, testing, improving, developing, deploying, commercializing, operating, or otherwise using any AI/ML System with, on, using, or in connection with Covered Software;

   使用受覆盖软件、以受覆盖软件为对象、与受覆盖软件一起或与受覆盖软件有关，训练、微调、对齐、评估、验证、测试、改进、开发、部署、商业化、运行或以其他方式使用任何 AI/ML 系统；

2. using, copying, accessing, processing, incorporating, transforming, adapting, compiling, analyzing, indexing, embedding, caching, logging, or otherwise exploiting Covered Software for or in connection with any AI/ML System;

   为任何 AI/ML 系统或与任何 AI/ML 系统有关，使用、复制、访问、处理、并入、转换、适配、编译、分析、索引、嵌入、缓存、记录或以其他方式利用受覆盖软件；

3. including, embedding, exposing, providing, reproducing, distributing, transmitting, serving, making available, or otherwise using Covered Software as source code, training material, reference material, retrieval content, prompt content, generated content, product content, product component, service component, dataset, corpus, benchmark, input material, output material, or evaluation material of or for any AI/ML System;

   将受覆盖软件作为任何 AI/ML 系统的源代码、训练材料、参考材料、检索内容、提示内容、生成内容、产品内容、产品组件、服务组件、数据集、语料库、基准、输入材料、输出材料或评估材料而纳入、嵌入、公开、提供、复制、分发、传输、服务化、使其可获得或以其他方式使用；

4. submitting, uploading, transmitting, exposing, indexing, embedding, caching, logging, processing, analyzing, inferring on, transforming, or otherwise making Covered Software available to any hosted model, coding assistant, retrieval system, embedding service, evaluation service, data-labeling service, cloud platform, contractor, subcontractor, API provider, or other third-party system or service, whether or not such third party retains, trains on, logs, reviews, caches, or claims not to use the submitted material; or

   向任何托管模型、代码助手、检索系统、嵌入服务、评估服务、数据标注服务、云平台、承包商、分包商、API 提供方或其他第三方系统或服务提交、上传、传输、暴露、索引、嵌入、缓存、记录、处理、分析、推断、转换或以其他方式提供受覆盖软件，无论该第三方是否保留、用于训练、记录、审阅、缓存或声称不使用提交材料；或

5. creating, retaining, using, distributing, sublicensing, commercializing, or making available any dataset, corpus, benchmark, prompt set, retrieval index, embedding, vector database, model, checkpoint, adapter, weight, fine-tune, distillation, evaluation result, synthetic data, generated output, product component, or other artifact created by, incorporating, trained on, fine-tuned on, evaluated against, prompted with, retrieved from, substantially derived from, or otherwise derived from Covered Software.

   创建、保留、使用、分发、再许可、商业化或使任何数据集、语料库、基准、提示集、检索索引、嵌入、向量数据库、模型、检查点、适配器、权重、微调结果、蒸馏结果、评估结果、合成数据、生成输出、产品组件或其他制品可获得，而该等材料是由受覆盖软件创建、包含受覆盖软件、基于受覆盖软件训练、微调、评估、提示、检索、实质性衍生或以其他方式衍生自受覆盖软件。

"Restricted Use" means any Restricted AI Use by a Restricted Person; any Restricted AI Use for, on behalf of, at the known direction or express instruction of, under funding from, under control of, for delivery to, or for the substantial benefit of a Restricted Person, including where a Restricted Person is a known, intended, probable, reasonably foreseeable, or commercially targeted recipient, customer, integration target, acquirer, licensee, user, or beneficiary; any preparatory, enabling, staging, conversion, cleaning, summarization, indexing, embedding, evaluation, or routing act undertaken with knowledge or reason to know that Covered Software will be used in a Restricted AI Use; and any attempt to cause, enable, assist, procure, outsource, route, conceal, or facilitate any such activity.

“受限使用”指由受限主体进行的任何受限 AI 使用；为受限主体、代表受限主体、按受限主体已知指令或明确指令、在受限主体资助下、在受限主体控制下、向受限主体交付或为受限主体实质利益而进行的任何受限 AI 使用，包括受限主体是已知、预期、很可能、可合理预见或商业上被定向作为接收方、客户、集成目标、收购方、被许可方、用户或受益人的情形；在明知或有理由知道受覆盖软件将被用于受限 AI 使用的情况下实施的任何准备、促成、暂存、转换、清洗、摘要、索引、嵌入、评估或路由行为；以及任何导致、促成、协助、采购、外包、路由、隐匿或便利该等行为的尝试。

"Restricted Artifacts" means any dataset, corpus, benchmark, prompt set, retrieval index, embedding, vector database, model, checkpoint, adapter, weight, fine-tune, distillation, evaluation result, synthetic data, generated output, product component, or other artifact created through or for a Restricted Use by, incorporating, trained on, fine-tuned on, evaluated against, prompted with, retrieved from, substantially derived from, or otherwise derived from Covered Software, to the extent such artifact contains, encodes, preserves, reproduces, is substantially derived from, is used as a substitute for expressive content of the Software, or materially preserves, implements, enables, emulates, operationalizes, or extracts protected capabilities, behavior, decision rules, representations, or learned parameters from Covered Software, regardless of human-readable expression.

“受限制品”指任何通过或为了受限使用而由受覆盖软件创建、包含受覆盖软件、基于受覆盖软件训练、微调、评估、提示、检索、实质性衍生或以其他方式衍生自受覆盖软件的数据集、语料库、基准、提示集、检索索引、嵌入、向量数据库、模型、检查点、适配器、权重、微调结果、蒸馏结果、评估结果、合成数据、生成输出、产品组件或其他制品，但仅限于该制品包含、编码、保留、复制、实质性衍生自、被用作本软件表达内容替代品，或实质性保留、实施、启用、模拟、运行化或提取受覆盖软件受保护的能力、行为、决策规则、表示或学习参数的范围，无论其是否具有人类可读表达。

### 3. Prohibited Uses / 禁止使用

No person may engage in a Restricted Use.

任何人均不得进行受限使用。

Access, receipt, possession, retention, internal evaluation, internal testing, or internal processing for a Restricted Use is itself a Restricted Use.

为受限使用而访问、接收、持有、保留、内部评估、内部测试或内部处理，本身即构成受限使用。

No Restricted Person may access, possess, receive, use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, sell, host, process, or otherwise exploit Covered Software for any Restricted Use.

任何受限主体均不得为任何受限使用而访问、持有、接收、使用、复制、修改、合并、发布、分发、再许可、销售、托管、处理或以其他方式利用受覆盖软件。

A person that becomes a Restricted Person after obtaining Covered Software may not continue any access, retention, use, exploitation, service access, cached copy, backup, descendant, or related Restricted Artifact for or in connection with any Restricted Use.

任何人在取得受覆盖软件后成为受限主体的，不得为任何受限使用或与任何受限使用有关，继续访问、保留、使用、利用、服务访问、缓存副本、备份、后代材料或相关受限制品。

A person is responsible for Restricted Uses performed by its affiliates, agents, contractors, subcontractors, service providers, customers, users, systems, or any other person acting on its behalf, at its direction, under its control, or for its benefit.

任何人应对其关联方、代理人、承包商、分包商、服务提供方、客户、用户、系统或任何代表其、按其指示、在其控制下或为其利益行事的人所进行的受限使用负责。

### 4. Closed-Source, Modified, and Hosted Uses / 闭源、修改及托管使用

